  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Keywords: Bukijutsu, Finisher, Clash, Earth Release</p><p>You begin to collect and manifest earth release chakra until it laces the striking portion of your weapon. The earth release chakra begins to magnify the weight and striking power of your attacks allowing you crush anything in your path is little difficulty.</p><p>Select one creature you can see within range as you fire multiple attacks into the air and quickly quadruple the weight of your attacks causing them to fall back to the earth while homing in on them. Make 2 ranged taijutsu attacks, dealing your weapons damage die + 3d8 additional damage die in earth damage.</p><p>A creature you hit with 2 or more attacks using this jutsu must make a Strength saving throw as you disable one of their legs (your choice) on a failed save. A creature with a disabled leg in this way cannot move effectively, causing them to be unable to cast jutsu with a Mobility (M) component, Dash, dodge, disengage or move while prone. A jutsu which removes conditions cast at B-Rank or higher can restore the disabled leg.</p>",
